---
title: Lemony Parmesan Shrimp Salad Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: This simple salad is packed with bright flavors and crisp textures for a light, satisfying meal. You’ll start by sizzling up quick-cooking garlic-herb shrimp to top refreshing baby lettuce tossed with juicy tomatoes and crunchy croutons in a creamy, Parmesan-infused Greek dressing. Garnish with more shredded Parm, and serve with a side of buttery garlic bread pan-toasted to golden perfection (the perfect accompaniment for swiping up any extra dressing).
